# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CODEOWNERS
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Defines who is responsible for specific parts of this repository.
# GitHub uses this file to automatically request reviews from code owners.
#
# Format:
#   <file pattern>   <owner>
# Owners can be:
#   @username or @organization/team
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Enforcement:
# To enforce code owner approvals:
# 1. Go to: Settings → Branches → Branch Protection Rules.
# 2. Enable “Require review from Code Owners.”
# 3. Add "@StaytunedLLP/codeowners" as the required reviewer team.
# This enables dynamic membership control—no file edits needed for member changes.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------


